title: 10 Endrathukkulla Song Teaser: Aanalum Intha Mayakkam
text:
The song teaser of Vikram's Aanalum Intha Mayakkam from the film 10 Endrathukkulla was released recently. The music label posted on its micro-blogging page, "It's here! Presenting #AanaalumIndhaMayakkam song teaser from #10Endrathukulla starring #Vikram @Samanthaprabhu2." Click here for the link to the song.
Stay updated on the go with Times of India News App. Click here to download it for your device.
